        "when": "2026-04",
        "text": "Jenny was an absolute joy to work with from start to finish, and we couldn’t be happier with our experience! She made us feel so comfortable and relaxed in front of the camera - which really shows in how natural and genuine both our engagement and wedding photos turned out.\n\nJenny’s experience with locations around Vail Valley was invaluable—she knew exactly where to go to capture the most stunning backdrops and lighting, and she truly got us the best shots we could have imagined. Not only is she incredibly talented, but she’s also kind, professional, and genuinely invested in her clients. We feel so lucky to have worked with her, thank you!!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2025-07",
        "text": "Hiring Jenny as our wedding photographer was one of the best decisions we made! From our first conversation to the final gallery delivery, she was professional, warm, organized, and genuinely passionate about their work.\n\nOn the day of the wedding, Jenny somehow managed to be everywhere without ever being intrusive. She captured the even the tiniest details in addition to the big special moments. She was such a calming presence and really made us and our families feel so comfortable.\n\nWe’ve received countless compliments on our pictures, and I  feel like I'm reliving the day when I scroll through the gallery. If you’re lucky enough to book Nate and Jenny, know that you’ll be in the best hands. Can’t recommend them highly enough!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2017-10",
        "text": "We loved using Nate and Jenny for our engagement & wedding photos!! We are not super comfortable in front of the camera and they made it all feel so natural and fun. Our day was perfect and the pictures are amazing. You want good pictures of your important day and we have SOOO many amazing ones. We are super lucky to have worked with them.\n\nMore recently, Jenny has shot some pictures of our family for Christmas cards and also pregnancy shots.. she's amazing and so good with kids!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2022-07",
        "text": "Nate and Jenny are the absolute BEST! Not only are they wonderful to work with, respectful, and FUN, they are immensely talented and clearly love what they do. Chris and I got married on an 18 degree NYE day. Jenny was the best cheerleader as we stood out in the cold for some amazing shots. She was efficient, decisive, and got all of the shots we wanted (and then some!) with our family and various groups of friends.\n\nNate and Jenny have also photographed the weddings of two of my sisters. Our photos are different, special, and unique to our personalities and events.\n\nWe love Nate and Jenny and proudly consider them dear friends. You truly cannot find a better photographer duo than these two who have mastered the art of capturing spirit, joy, and hope in a moment."
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2017-10",
        "text": "I cannot recommend Nate and Jenny enough!  Hiring a photographer for my wedding day was my number one priority when it came to my vendor list and I was not willing to sacrifice on quality.  Their level of professionalism, kindness, and attention to detail is beyond compare and my Husband and I look forward to our Anniversary each year because we sit down and look through all our wedding pictures they captured.  Our photos are displayed throughout our home and we cannot put a price tag on those memories.  Nate and Jenny, we are so grateful for you both personally and professionally!  Thank you for being an integral part of our wedding!  We love you!"
      }
